<!DOCTYPE tmc-service-paragraph SYSTEM "../dtd/paragraph-contents.dtd">
<tmc-service-paragraph><pub id="RM25T0E"><servcat id="_51"><name>Engine / Hybrid System</name><section id="_029760"><name>1VD-FTV ENGINE CONTROL</name><ttl id="_0282525"><name>ECD SYSTEM(w/ DPF)</name><para id="RM100000000ZRIM" category="C"><dtccode>P0489</dtccode><dtcname>Exhaust Gas Recirculation Control Circuit Low</dtcname><dtccode>P0490</dtccode><dtcname>Exhaust Gas Recirculation Control Circuit High</dtcname><subpara id="RM100000000ZRIM_01" category="03"><name>DESCRIPTION</name><content5><ptxt>The EGR actuator is operated by the ECM and opens and closes the EGR valve using gears. The opening angle of the EGR valve is detected by the EGR position sensor, which is mounted on the electric EGR control valve assembly.</ptxt><table type="dtc-explan-table" pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="6"><colspec colname="1" colwidth="0.71in"/><colspec colname="2" colwidth="1.13in"/><colspec colname="3" colwidth="1.91in"/><colspec colname="4" colwidth="1.91in"/><colspec colname="5" colwidth="0.71in"/><colspec colname="6" colwidth="0.71in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Detection Item</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC Detection Condition</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Trouble Area</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>MIL</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Memory</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-code"><ptxt>P0489</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="detect-item"><ptxt>Exhaust Gas Recirculation Control Circuit Low</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-detect-cond"><ptxt>Both of the following conditions are met for 2.0 seconds (1 trip detection logic):</ptxt><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>The EGR actuator duty cycle is 80% or higher.</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>EGR actuator current is below 0.5 A.</ptxt></item></list1></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="trouble-area"><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>Open or short in EGR actuator circuit</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>Electric EGR control valve assembly</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>ECM</ptxt></item></list1></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="mil"><ptxt>Comes on</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="memory"><ptxt>DTC stored</ptxt></data-name></entry></row><row><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-code"><ptxt>P0490</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="detect-item"><ptxt>Exhaust Gas Recirculation Control Circuit High</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-detect-cond"><ptxt>An EGR actuator current of 8 A or higher or the ECM internal circuit temperature of 150 to 160°C (302 to 320°F) or higher is detected.</ptxt><ptxt>(1 trip detection logic)</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="trouble-area"><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>Open or short in EGR actuator assembly circuit</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>Electric EGR control valve assembly</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>ECM</ptxt></item></list1></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="mil"><ptxt>Comes on</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="memory"><ptxt>DTC stored</ptxt></data-name></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><table pgwide="1"><title>Related Data List</title><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="3.54in"/><colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="3.54in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Data List</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>P0489</ptxt></entry><entry morerows="1" valign="middle"><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>Actual EGR Valve Pos</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>Target EGR Valve Pos</ptxt></item></list1></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>P0490</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000ZRIM_07" category="03"><name>CONFIRMATION DRIVING PATTERN</name><content5><table pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="2.12in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="4.96in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>DTC Detection Drive Pattern</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>P0489</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" morerows="1"><ptxt>Idle the engine for 5 seconds or more</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>P0490</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000ZRIM_03" category="03"><name>WIRING DIAGRAM</name><content5><ptxt>Refer to DTC P0405</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000ZRI9"/></mlink></ptxt></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000ZRIM_04" category="10"><name>CAUTION / NOTICE / HINT</name><content5><atten3><ptxt>After replacing the ECM, the new ECM needs registration (Click here <mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000Z1DB"/></mlink>) and initialization (Click here <mlink><xref label="Seep00002" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000YXU9"/></mlink>).</ptxt></atten3><atten4><ptxt>Read freeze frame data using the GTS. Freeze frame data records the engine condition when malfunctions are detected. When troubleshooting, freeze frame data can help determine if the vehicle was moving or stationary, if the engine was warmed up or not, and other data from the time the malfunction occurred.</ptxt></atten4></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000ZRIM_06" category="01"><name>PROCEDURE</name><testgrp id="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0001" cellposition="1-1"><testtitle>INSPECT ELECTRIC EGR CONTROL VALVE ASSEMBLY (RESISTANCE OF EGR ACTUATOR)</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Remove the electric EGR control valve assembly.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM1000000010803"/></mlink></ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Measure the resistance according to the value(s) in the table below.</ptxt><spec type="other"><title>Standard resistance</title><table><tgroup cols="3"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.38in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.38in"/><colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.37in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Condition</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>5 (M-) - 4 (M+)</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Always</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>No short or open circuit</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec><figure type="1" translate="C"><graphic graphicname="A351114C01" width="3.434793307in" height="2.192421260in"/><callout><table pgwide="0" type="caption-table"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="0.69in"/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="2.75in"/><tbody><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>*a</ptxt></entry><entry><ptxt>Component without harness connected</ptxt><ptxt>(Electric EGR Control Valve Assembly)</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></callout></figure></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>OK</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>NG</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="1-1"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="2-1" childid="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0002"/></result><result label="2" cellposition="1-3"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="2-3" childid="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0008"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0002" cellposition="2-1"><testtitle>CHECK HARNESS AND CONNECTOR (ELECTRIC EGR CONTROL VALVE ASSEMBLY - ECM)</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Disconnect the electric EGR control valve assembly connector.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Disconnect the ECM connector.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Measure the resistance according to the value(s) in the table below.</ptxt><spec type="other"><title>Standard resistance</title><table pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="3"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="3.54in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.77in"/><colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.77in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Condition</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>C106-4 (M+) - C39-86 (EGM+)</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Always</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Below 1 Ω</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>C106-5 (M-) - C39-85 (EGM-)</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Always</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Below 1 Ω</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>C106-4 (M+) or C39-86 (EGM+) - Body ground and other terminals</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Always</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>10 kΩ or higher</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>C106-5 (M-) or C39-85 (EGM-) - Body ground and other terminals</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Always</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>10 kΩ or higher</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></test1><test1><ptxt>Reconnect the electric EGR control valve assembly connector.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Reconnect the ECM connector.</ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>OK</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>NG</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="2-1"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="3-1" childid="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0003"/></result><result label="2" cellposition="2-2"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="3-2" childid="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0005"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0003" cellposition="3-1"><testtitle>REPLACE ECM</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Replace the ECM.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="001" term-id-to="003" href="RM100000000FJHY"/><xref term-id-from="003" href="RM1000000013IGX"/></mlink></ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="3-1"><action actiontype="jump" cellposition="4-1" childid="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0006"><actiontitle>GO TO STEP 5</actiontitle></action></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0005" cellposition="3-2"><testtitle>REPAIR OR REPLACE HARNESS OR CONNECTOR</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Repair or replace the harness or connector.</ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="3-2"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="4-2" childid="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0006"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0006" cellposition="4-2"><testtitle>CONFIRM WHETHER MALFUNCTION HAS BEEN SUCCESSFULLY REPAIRED</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Connect the GTS to the DLC3.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Clear the DTCs.</ptxt><gts-info category="dtc-delete"><title>Powertrain &gt; Engine and ECT &gt; Clear DTCs</title><gts-exec function-id="50002"><gts-ecu ecu-id="234"/></gts-exec><app-communication><app-param name="process-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="edit-mode">1</app-param><app-param name="insert-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="function-tab">0</app-param><app-param name="category-div">1</app-param><app-param name="category-div-name">Powertrain</app-param><app-param name="ecu-id">234</app-param><app-param name="ecu-name">Engine and ECT</app-param><app-param name="gts-order">0</app-param><app-param name="selected-state">1</app-param></app-communication></gts-info></test1><test1><ptxt>Turn the ignition switch off for 30 seconds or more.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Start the engine.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Idle the engine for 5 seconds or more</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Enter the following menus: Powertrain / Engine and ECT / Trouble Codes.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Confirm that the DTC is not output again.</ptxt><gts-info category="dtc-read"><title>Powertrain &gt; Engine and ECT &gt; Trouble Codes</title><gts-exec function-id="50001"><gts-ecu ecu-id="234"/></gts-exec><app-communication><app-param name="process-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="edit-mode">1</app-param><app-param name="insert-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="function-tab">0</app-param><app-param name="category-div">1</app-param><app-param name="category-div-name">Powertrain</app-param><app-param name="ecu-id">234</app-param><app-param name="ecu-name">Engine and ECT</app-param><app-param name="gts-order">0</app-param><app-param name="selected-state">0</app-param></app-communication></gts-info></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="4-2"><action actiontype="end" cellposition="5-2"><actiontitle>END</actiontitle><content6/></action></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0008" cellposition="2-3"><testtitle>REPLACE ELECTRIC EGR CONTROL VALVE ASSEMBLY</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Replace the electric EGR control valve assembly.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM1000000010803"/></mlink></ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="2-3"><action actiontype="jump" cellposition="3-3" childid="RM100000000ZRIM_06_0006"><actiontitle>GO TO STEP 5</actiontitle></action></result></results></testgrp></subpara></para></ttl></section></servcat></pub></tmc-service-paragraph>